data.description: Come home to beautiful Horse Creek Ridge a community of Fallbrook. The first level of the home offers an open concept with a stunning kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Downstairs you will find one bedroom and a half bathroom. Home has LVP throughout living area and upgraded carpeting in bedrooms. Laundry room is located upstairs along with two more bedrooms and master suite. The backyard is an entertainers delight offering a sparkling pool with stairs that lead up to a sunning deck. Just below is a BBQ island that offers a round bar for seating. The home has smart home features including a water filtration system and solar. The community offers 8 parks, running trails and  a clubhouse with a pool. This home will not disappoint even the pickiest of buyers.
